## Current Portfolio Posture

The Axodus ecosystem is a local/mock/read-only portfolio with several mature contractual or planning subtracks, but no production-authorized execution track.

No nucleus is classified as L7. No nucleus has production-ready authority for treasury, settlement, trading, swaps, payouts, wallet signing, on-chain writes, marketplace minting/value transfer, or production credentials.

